                        "ProjectMissionDescription": {
                            "val": "The Apache Capabilities Enhancements (ACE) prioritizes, informs, influences, matures, tracks, statuses, and packages technologies and\/or material solutions to address known capability gaps, identified during real-world combat missions and associated with current\/emerging threats; for transition to Apache development for integration and implementation to the AH-64E fleet to increase combat capability."
